description: Nottingham Forest: Champions League or FA Cup poll
title: Nottingham Forest: Champions League or FA Cup poll
title_page: Nottingham Forest: Champions League or FA Cup poll - BBC Sport
maintext:
Former West Ham and Aston Villa midfielder Nigel Reo-Coker believes "nine out of 10" Nottingham Forest fans would rather qualify for the Champions League than the FA Cup.
But, do you agree?
And, for the purposes of this poll, achieving both is simply not an option...
